@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_tawmka(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.sin(v2 + 0.94)) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.80 / v0 + 0.57)))
    v2 = v1
    v1 = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.54 - tmp + 0.29) - (v1 + 0.81 / v0 + 0.57)))
    tmp = (v2 - (wp.abs(v0 + 0.23) + (v0 + 0.74 + v1 + 0.76)))
    data[tid] = v0
